title: (Fri Early) Bobby’s Mailbag: Couple Bought a House with Dog Buried in Yard + Fun Fact Friday: Why Frogs Were the Best Pregnancy Tests + Friday Easy Trivia!
itunes:title: (Fri Early) Bobby’s Mailbag: Couple Bought a House with Dog Buried in Yard + Fun Fact Friday: Why Frogs Were the Best Pregnancy Tests + Friday Easy Trivia!
description:
Bobby helps out a listener who needs advice on what to do after they bought a new home and the previous honor left a statue for their dog who is buried in the yard. Amy shares her 5 fun facts including one about why the best pregnancy test was a frog until just recently! And we play our weekly game of Easy Trivia!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
